<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavaruṣaṁbulu 130<unclear>2</unclear> gunēṁṭi
<lb n="2"/>śrāvaṇa śukla dvitīyanu Ādivāramunā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁḍu gayiṇiveḷuḍāna dāsinaya
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ni Anavōtanāyani mahādēvi kana 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ku<unclear>lakṣmī</unclear> tanaku Abhīṣṭārttasiddhigānu
<lb n="6"/>śrīnarāsihyanathuniki nityamu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nnu sannidhini mapaṭi dhupaAvasara
<lb n="8" break="no"/>Aṁdu tiruvaḷikakōla veluṁguṭaku ga
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁḍḍamāḍalu AIdu 5 peṭṭi kuṁca
<lb n="10" break="no"/>prasādamu ṭhā<unclear>vu</unclear>gā paṭṭi Appamunā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yaka vallabhanna koḍuku śrīrāmanna
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ku peṭṭenu Ītaṁḍu Ī prasādamu bhuji
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁci Ī divyakōla kolupu ĀcaṁdrārkkastaĪ
<lb n="14" break="no"/>(Ī)gā koluvaṁgālāṁḍu Ī dharmmu śrīvaiṣṇava
<lb n="15"/>rakṣa śrīśrīśrī
</p>

